        <div class="proyectos">
            <h1 class="display_text">Las Aventuras del Intrépido Cacao</h1>
            <svg class="ani-icon" width="280" height="300" viewBox="0 0 480 512"><path fill="currentColor" d="M471.99 334.43L336.06 256l135.93-78.43c7.66-4.42 10.28-14.2 5.86-21.86l-32.02-55.43c-4.42-7.65-14.21-10.28-21.87-5.86l-135.93 78.43V16c0-8.84-7.17-16-16.01-16h-64.04c-8.84 0-16.01 7.16-16.01 16v156.86L56.04 94.43c-7.66-4.42-17.45-1.79-21.87 5.86L2.15 155.71c-4.42 7.65-1.8 17.44 5.86 21.86L143.94 256L8.01 334.43c-7.66 4.42-10.28 14.21-5.86 21.86l32.02 55.43c4.42 7.65 14.21 10.27 21.87 5.86l135.93-78.43V496c0 8.84 7.17 16 16.01 16h64.04c8.84 0 16.01-7.16 16.01-16V339.14l135.93 78.43c7.66 4.42 17.45 1.8 21.87-5.86l32.02-55.43c4.42-7.65 1.8-17.43-5.86-21.85"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="content-description">Animation •  Character Design •  Graphic Design // Koolch</div>

        <div class="experience-container proyectos">
            <div class="experience">
                <h2>Description</h2>
            </div>
            <p>This animated series is a fun, cartoonish way to <span class="text-span">teach kids about healthy snacking,</span> aiming to instill good eating habits through engaging characters and stories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="experience-container proyectos">
            <div class="experience">
                <h2>Technologies</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Ilustrator • Photoshop • After Effects</p>
        </div>
        <div class="experience-container proyectos">
            <div class="experience">
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=40OqNmCiido" target="_blank">Link
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="m12 4.5l-5 5m5-5l5 5m-5-5v10c0 1.667 1 5 5 5"/></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <img class="image-large" src="../images/one_cacao.avif" alt="Imagen del Intrépido Cacao y su equipo reunido peleando contra los dulces malvados">
    </section>

    <section class="section full-width" style="background-image: url('../images/Collage_koolch.avif');">
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <img class="image-large" src="/images/portada_cacao.avif"></img>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <video loop autoplay muted playsinline class="image-large" src="../videos/koolch.webm"></video>
    </section>
</Layout>